1 likes, 0 comments - thecelebpost_tcp on July 31, 2023: "In the latest blow to Britney Spears, it emerged that her two sons are relocating to Hawaii with their father, her ex, Kevin Federline.

According to TMZ, the singerâ€™s children have scheduled their big move from LA on Thursday but have no plans on seeing their mother to say goodbye.

Federline, who has sole custody of Sean Preston and Jayden, is making the big move with his wife Victoria Prince.

The family will reportedly move to a rented property while they search for their permanent home.

According to sources, Federline encouraged Jayden and Sean to meet their mother before leaving but has not been pushing his kids to do say.

Sources add that Federline is "relieved" that Spears has not taken him to court over the move, adding that she likely feels she has done "the right thing" by letting her sons move on.
